snippet.textDisplay: I think VAR should be an option that managers can use during the match. It will be something like hawk eye in tennis. If a manager believes that a decision is wrong, he will request for a VAR review. If it turns out that the manager is right, the decision will be changed. If the manager is wrong, then he can no longer use VAR again for the rest of the match. This system could be more fair and entertaining for sure.
snippet.textOriginal: I think VAR should be an option that managers can use during the match. It will be something like hawk eye in tennis. If a manager believes that a decision is wrong, he will request for a VAR review. If it turns out that the manager is right, the decision will be changed. If the manager is wrong, then he can no longer use VAR again for the rest of the match. This system could be more fair and entertaining for sure.
